511
00:44:38.040 --> 00:44:40.964
Tobin Capp's Dalmatian.
the pets were never found. None of them.

512
00:44:41.120 --> 00:44:43.043
Do you remember Mason toward the end?

513
00:44:43.240 --> 00:44:46.449
