into false memories.

534
00:45:36.720 --> 00:45:39.200
You saw Mom put the dog
in the office on a number of occasions.

535
00:45:39.320 --> 00:45:40.731
My God. what did they do to you?

536
00:45:40.920 --> 00:45:43.280
