00:51:42.360 --> 00:51:44.044
There it is.

636
00:52:05.000 --> 00:52:06.570
Ha!

637
00:52:07.160 --> 00:52:08.286
Yes.

638
00:52:08.960 --> 00:52:10.121
Yes!

639
00:52:11.520 --> 00:52:12.726
Yes!

640
00:52:13.600 --> 00:52:15.204
Yes. Yes.

641
00:52:15.400 --> 00:52:17.607
Yes. Yes!

