<i>It was a bad marriage.
Look how it ended up.</i>

645
00:52:34.880 --> 00:52:37.201
<i>Our father was a cheater.
and it drove our mother crazy.</i>

646
00:52:37.360 --> 00:52:38.850
<i>- Stop it.
- He snapped and he killed her.</i>

647
